{"lastModified":1774619368203,"uri":"c::18231584005::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: \nSummer: Greece\nWinter: Caribbean\n\nIntroducing Sunmoon, an exquisite Alegria 67 luxury catamaran that promises to make your cruising experience unforgettable. This sleek and stylish beauty features five elegant cabins, including one master and four queen bed cabins, perfect for accommodating up to ten guests in ultimate comfort and luxury. Sunmoon's sophisticated design boasts an impressive range of amenities, with plenty of space to relax and enjoy the stunning sea views. The yacht's spacious saloon is perfect for indoor dining and is equipped with a 4K 50-inch UHD Smart TV, Bose sound system, and comfortable seating for all guests. The state-of-the-art galley is fully equipped with high-end appliances, and elegant furnishings add a touch of luxury and refinement throughout the yacht's interior. Outside, the voluminous deck space is ideal for outdoor dining, cocktails, or lounging in the sun. The flybridge features a large sunbathing area and is perfect for taking in the beautiful views while enjoying the breeze. The yacht also has an onboard BBQ grill and wet bar perfect for socializing and entertaining. For those looking to explore the water further, Sunmoon offers plenty of exciting water toys, including Snorkeling Gear, Kayaks, Stand-Up Paddleboards, wakeboard, water Skis, fishing equipment, and many others. The vessel is also equipped with a hydraulic swim platform for easy access to the water. Sunmoon is operated by a highly skilled and experienced crew of three, including a captain, a chef, and a stewardess. The crew is professional, friendly, and dedicated to ensuring that all guests receive exceptional service throughout their stay. Whether you're looking to lay back and soak up the sun, indulge in gourmet cuisine, or explore the sea's many treasures, Sunmoon promises an unforgettable luxury yacht charter experience.","blueprint":{"name":"SUNMOON","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c39f03a0-b7fa-11ef-b8b1-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c377f3a0-b7fa-11ef-b8b0-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c3a0d860-b7fa-11ef-b8b1-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c3a08a41-b7fa-11ef-b8b1-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c39b8130-b7fa-11ef-b8b1-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c3a01510-b7fa-11ef-b8b1-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c39ba840-b7fa-11ef-b8b0-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c36492b0-b7fa-11ef-b8b0-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c3a25f00-b7fa-11ef-b8b1-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c39f78d0-b7fa-11ef-b8b1-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c3a08a40-b7fa-11ef-b8b1-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c3a237f0-b7fa-11ef-b8b1-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c39fc6f0-b7fa-11ef-b8b1-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c3a1c2c0-b7fa-11ef-b8b1-6f32c8e04075/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d2596d30-4352-11ef-bff8-67cccb3db38f::assets::c36